      "timestamp": "2026-06-15",
      "error_message": "Hebrew commands phrased as infinitives (\"לדבר עם הפנסיונר\", \"לקחת עיתון\") or with a small verb typo (\"דברר\") fell through to a random snark instead of acting.",
      "file": "js/engine/parser.js",
      "root_cause": "parse() matched the first token only against an exact verb-synonym list; it never stripped the infinitive ל- prefix and had no fuzzy fallback, so any unlisted conjugation/typo produced verb=null.",
      "fix": "Added verbOf(): exact -> strip leading prefix letter (infinitive ל / stray ו) -> Levenshtein distance<=1 fallback. Also added suggestVerb() for a 'did you mean' hint and general Hebrew prefix-form + fuzzy noun matching (scoreName/matchScore).",
