      "error_message": "E2E regression: 'אכול ריבה' stopped triggering the jam death; scene12.onCommand intercepted it with the knitting line.",
      "file": "js/engine/parser.js",
      "root_cause": "New fuzzy matchNoun let 'ריבה' match 'סריגה' at edit-distance 2 (4-letter word). scene12.onCommand uses RHParser.matchNoun for scenery (['סריגה','מסרגות','סוודר']), so it falsely claimed the command before the jam hotspot/item could.",
